723716f-a.title: Manhattan: Varick Street - North Moore Street
723716f-a.text:
Varick Street, west side, north from North Moore Street, to Ericsson Place (Beach Street), showing under construction an addition to the Merchant's Refrigerating Company. Also seen on the left, are Nos. 27 to 37 North Moore, adjoining and west of the N.W. corner of Varick Streets. These three buildings comprise the original home of the Merchant's Refrigerating Co. The 3-story building on the right, is the 4th Precinct Police Station.
NNEG ~ Y38S  January 22, 1925.
Camera Craft.
